    <title>The Call for Participation has concluded.</title>
    <link href="https://libregraphicsmeeting.org/2025/news/2025-02-02_0001-closed-call-for-participation/" />
    <updated>2025-02-02T00:00:00Z</updated>
    <id>https://libregraphicsmeeting.org/2025/news/2025-02-02_0001-closed-call-for-participation/</id>
    <content type="html">
    &lt;p class=&quot;lead&quot;&gt;Some slots will still be available. Read here about our next steps.
&lt;/p&gt;
